---

<section class="relative border-t border-edge/40 py-32">
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute left-0 top-0 h-px w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-accent/20 to-transparent"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-12">
      <!-- Label column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4">
        <span
          class="font-display text-xs font-600 tracking-widest text-accent uppercase"
          >Speaker Profile</span
        >
        <h2
          class="mt-4 font-display text-4xl font-800 leading-tight tracking-tight text-ivory sm:text-5xl"
        >
          Built by<br />
          <span class="text-subtle">practitioners.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Content column -->
      <div class="space-y-8 lg:col-span-7 lg:col-start-6">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-subtle">
          Our speakers are not professional keynote-givers. They are engineers, founders, and technical leaders who are actively building — sharing real lessons from real work. Expect raw, unfiltered takes on architecture, scaling, hiring, and the challenges of operating across two ecosystems.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-subtle">
          Past and future speakers come from companies shaping how software is built and delivered at scale.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
